{"tid":2211911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇白禮頓個教練對Jahanbakhsh咁有成見？","createTime":"2020-09-21T11:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T10:40:31.000Z","uid":34899,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"73aa48a781b06db028567718443ec1be8180386c","tid":2211911,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"無論查漢巴殊喺前一場比賽做得幾好<br />\n例如上季連續兩場入波 窄角度爆射+倒掛<br />\n定係今季盃賽正選一傳一射做到MOM<br />\n個教練之後都照樣對佢投閒置散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似啱啱對紐卡素場波<br />\n明明一早領先到二比零<br />\n唔明點解唔早啲換出黎<br />\n要去到完場前先比幾分鐘去侮辱佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當佢真係無表現踢廿分鐘<br />\n咁都係位換位啫 又唔關條防線事<br />\n又唔會令後面即刻比人追和到<br />\n除左對佢有偏見之外諗唔到有其他原因要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f1c49de0b311d4f3f7d5821c788a8675251ad7","tid":2211911,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"因為伊朗比西方國家制裁囉 樓主咁都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff5bdca247c015779921ad1ec152df817310b5a","tid":2211911,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0f1c49de0b311d4f3f7d5821c788a8675251ad7","tid":2211911,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"因為伊朗比西方國家制裁囉 樓主咁都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"唔見葡超達利美會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\